Date: 2026-07-05
Author: Alfonso Cano
Maintainer: Alfonso Cano <alfonso.cano@correo.buap.mx>
Enhances: rkward
Description: An RKWard plugin to create dummy variables (one-hot
        encoding) from survey or dataframe objects using the
        'fastDummies' package. Supports unused level dropping and
        custom prefixing.
